{
  "controlWidth" : 12.0,
  "label" : "TextBlock9",
  "text" : "<div class=\"blue-info-wrapper\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem !important; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\">\n<div><span class=\"icon\"><img src=\"/resource/DFD_Blue_Info_icon\" alt=\"\" width=\"52\" height=\"52\" /></span></div>\n<div class=\"blue-info-text\">\n<p>Please upload a copy of alcohol vendor names in the Document Upload Section of this application. Must include name and contact information of ALL alcohol vendors. As the event organizer, you are responsible for making sure all of your alcohol vendors obtain the necessary permits to be compliant with state and local liquor laws. Traditionally each vendor needs a catering permit or a picnic license which can only be obtained once you receive your special event permit.</p>\n<br />\n<p>Any event with Alcohol requires security from a provider licensed in the City of St. Louis.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
  "show" : {
